## 2. Description of Service

StatsKey is a nutrition and fitness tracking application that provides:
- AI-powered food recognition and nutrition analysis
- Exercise and activity tracking
- Weight and body composition monitoring
- Integration with Apple HealthKit
- Cloud synchronization services

